{"id":11496,"date":"2021-08-18T15:40:34","date_gmt":"2021-08-18T08:40:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/eblog.vn\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership"},"modified":"2021-08-18T15:40:34","modified_gmt":"2021-08-18T08:40:34","slug":"chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft-Hyundai Membership"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"newdetails col-md-12 animated fadeInLeftBig \">\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng k\u00ednh ch\u00e0o qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch !<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t h\u00e0nh 3 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ebb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<br \/>\nKhi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i (t\u00f9y theo t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ebb) 3 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ebb bao g\u1ed3m:\u00a0\u00a0Th\u1ebb Silver\/B\u1ea1c, Th\u1ebb Gold\/V\u00e0ng, Th\u1ebb Platinum\/B\u1ea1ch Kim.<\/span>\n<\/p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11492\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e.jpeg\" width=\"1201\" height=\"629\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e.jpeg 1201w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e-240x126.jpeg 240w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e-540x283.jpeg 540w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e-300x157.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e-1024x536.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/chuong-trinh-khach-hang-than-thiet-hyundai-membership_611cc7850c21e-768x402.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1201px) 100vw, 1201px\" \/><br \/>\n\u00a0<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><u>1\/ H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tham gia v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p th\u1ebb<\/u><br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n\/T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu xe Hyundai \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n + th\u1ebb h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; M\u1ed7i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n\/th\u1ebb h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t 01 xe Hyundai. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p KH c\u00f3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u xe th\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n + th\u1ebb h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp v\u1edbi nhau.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebb trong v\u00f2ng t\u1eeb 10 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt h\u1ea1ng H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean m\u1edbi.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh th\u1ebb H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; C\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea5p th\u1ebb c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\t<\/tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:360px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:480px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:360px;height:36px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0&#8211; C\u1ea5p th\u1ebb m\u1edbi khi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<\/span><\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:480px;height:36px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">&#8211; Nh\u1eadp M\u1eabu \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd v\u00e0<br \/>\n\t\t\t&#8211; Cung c\u1ea5p b\u1ea3n ch\u1ee5p \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd xe v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n.<br \/>\n\t\t\tTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd xe -> cung\u00a0 c\u1ea5p b\u1ea3n sao h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng + s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:360px;height:70px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0&#8211; C\u1ea5p l\u1ea1i th\u1ebb khi H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t th\u1ebb (H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Hotline \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1ea1m kh\u00f3a th\u1ebb trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t th\u1ebb).<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:360px;height:35px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0&#8211; C\u1ea5p l\u1ea1i th\u1ebb khi H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean t\u0103ng\/xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:480px;height:35px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><u>2\/ X\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean<\/u><br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; Vi\u1ec7c x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1:\u00a0S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong k\u1ef3 x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; K\u1ef3 x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng: 12 th\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi m\u1edf th\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt h\u1ea1ng th\u1ebb m\u1edbi.<br \/>\n\u00a0 + X\u00e9t l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng: H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng ngay khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi (kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1edd t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 12 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e9t l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng)<br \/>\n\u00a0+ X\u00e9t Duy tr\u00ec ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng: khi \u0111\u1ee7 12 th\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi m\u1edf th\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt h\u1ea1ng th\u1ebb m\u1edbi, th\u1ebb h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i.<br \/>\n\u00a0+ N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: duy tr\u00ec h\u1ea1ng<br \/>\n\u00a0+ N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng duy tr\u00ec h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i: xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng li\u1ec1n d\u01b0\u1edbi<br \/>\n<u>3\/ T\u00edch l\u0169y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/u><br \/>\n\u00a0Sau khi H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng g\u1ecdi l\u00e0\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3m t\u00edch l\u0169y. \u0110i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u00f3 hai ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng:<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; \u0110i\u1ec3m t\u00edch l\u0169y d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng hay g\u1ecdi l\u00e0\u00a0\u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng. \u0110i\u1ec3m t\u00edch l\u0169y c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng ho\u1eb7c khi KH l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng, \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng s\u1ebd reset l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb 0.<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; \u0110i\u1ec3m t\u00edch l\u0169y ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng\/ chi tr\u1ea3 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1edf c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo hay g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.\u0110i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng\u00a0kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br \/>\n\u00a0T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m:<br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; 1 Vn\u0111\u00a0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 = 0.05 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch l\u0169y (c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng).<br \/>\n\u00a0<em>(*) Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m chi tr\u1ea3.<\/em><br \/>\n\u00a0&#8211; 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 VN\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1edf c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo<br \/>\n<u>V\u00ed\u00a0d\u1ee5:<\/u>\u00a0 &#8211;\u00a0 H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 thanh to\u00e1n 1 tri\u1ec7u vn\u0111 s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50 \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e9t h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 50,000 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.<br \/>\n\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&#8211; H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i 50,000 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ea5u tr\u1eeb 50,000 vn\u0111 v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chi tr\u1ea3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u1ea7n sau.<br \/>\n<u>4\/ \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng th\u1ebb<\/u><\/span><br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\t<\/tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:117px;height:34px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:384px;height:34px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n x\u00e9t l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:387px;height:34px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n x\u00e9t duy tr\u00ec h\u1ea1ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:117px;height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">SILVER<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:384px;height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">C\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1eeb 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t\/ 1 n\u0103m , doanh thu 2 tri\u1ec7u.<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:387px;height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-Lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:117px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">GOLD<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:384px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-L\u00e0 H\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7n Silver<br \/>\n\t\t\t-C\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t\/n\u0103m<br \/>\n\t\t\t-S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea1t 5 tri\u1ec7u<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:387px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-L\u00e0 H\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7n Silver<br \/>\n\t\t\t-C\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t\/n\u0103m<br \/>\n\t\t\t-s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea1t 5 tri\u1ec7u<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\">\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\t<\/tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:117px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">PLATINUM<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:384px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-L\u00e0 H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean Gold<br \/>\n\t\t\t-C\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t\/n\u0103m<br \/>\n\t\t\t-T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:387px;height:79px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">-L\u00e0 H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean Gold<br \/>\n\t\t\t-C\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 5 \u00a0l\u01b0\u1ee3t\/n\u0103m<br \/>\n\t\t\t-t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0(*) Ghi ch\u00fa:<br \/>\n\u00a0-01 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t sinh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb (doanh thu) >0 \u0111\u1ed3ng<br \/>\n\u00a0-Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n thanh to\u00e1n th\u00f4ng qua b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m.<br \/>\n<u>5\/ Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean<\/u><\/span><br \/>\n\u00a0<\/p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\t<\/tbody>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:202px;height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:126px;height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">SILVER<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:131px;height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">GOLD<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:167px;height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">PLATINUM<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:202px;height:28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1.T\u1eb7ng \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng (*) tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 5% doanh thu (kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thanh to\u00e1n qua b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m)<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:126px;height:28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3%<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:131px;height:28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">5%<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width:167px;height:28px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">10%<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:202px;height:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: